caption: Fentanyl concentrations in umbilical vein and maternal serum. Data are presented as mean (SD) or median [interquartile range] as appropriate
footnote: AUC, Area under the curve. Student's t test was used to calculate P‐values unless otherwise specified. Complete case analysis, numbers in some cells lower than the total numbers of patients included due to missing data (hemolysis of samples, technical laboratory difficulties). Mann–Whitney U test used. Data presented as median [25th; 75th percentile]. Two cases with missing data due to birth prior to 120 min sample.
